Usage: read_power_intent [-help] <fileName> {-cpf | -1801 | -msvDB}

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
<fileName>                          # input filename (string, required)
-1801                               # input file in IEEE1801 format
                                    # (bool, required)
-cpf                                # input file in CPF format (bool, required)
-msvDB                              # EDI IEEE1801 data file (.cpfdb)
                                    # (bool, required)